    "pseudocode":  "FLOW Microflow: ImporterHelper.SUB_ImportTemplateDocument\r\nNODES=14; EDGES=10\r\n1. START\r\n2. ACTION RetrieveAction: retrieve Template from ExcelImporter.Template\r\n3. DECISION has a template selected expression=$Template != empty\r\n4. BRANCH when EnumerationCase=true\r\n  5. ACTION JavaActionCallAction: call java action ExcelImporter.StartImportByTemplate -\u003e rowCount\r\n  6. BRANCH\r\n    7. ACTION ShowMessageAction: show message (text=The import is finished. {1} records have been imported., type=Information, blocking=true)\r\n    8. END\r\n  9. BRANCH on error\r\n    10. ACTION LogMessageAction: LogMessageAction (errorHandlingType=Rollback)\r\n    11. ACTION ShowMessageAction: show message (text=The following error occurred when importing document: {1} {2}, type=Error, blocking=true)\r\n    12. END\r\n13. BRANCH when EnumerationCase=false\r\n  14. ACTION ShowMessageAction: show message (text=No template selected for this file, type=Warning, blocking=true)\r\n  15. END",
